description: Netmore Group AB engages in the design of wireless networks. The company is headquartered in Stockholm, Stockholm and currently employs 33 full-time employees. The company went IPO on 2017-07-14. The firm offers customized solutions for wireless local networks with coverage for data and mobile communications. The company installs sells and maintains local private mobile and WiFi networks for indoor and outdoor use. The company also provides customers with telephone services via its own subscriber identification module (SIM) card nor.net. Also, the Company offers an integrated solution based on Tarifflex method, which enables to develop business support systems, such as billing and customer relationship management. The firm operates Netmore AB as subsidiary.
name: Netmore Group AB
